      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Well, where to start? A game full of promise that I feel compelled to mark down because it simply isn’t ready for the Nintendo Switch (at the time of writing, anyway). This could have been an 8 but had I scored it that way, I wouldn’t have been true to the stark reality of ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Hell Pie’s",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " performance issues. However, if ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Hell Pie ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "is patched, and let’s hope that it is, then I would seriously recommend it to any collectathon fans! Essentially, play this game, just not on Switch (yet).",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
